description:
The Cactus Blossoms share their experience working with David Lynch
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

In an interview on The Local Show on The Current, host Diane asks Page Burkum and Jack Torrey of the Cactus Blossoms what it was like to work with director David Lynch on the series "Twin Peaks." The Cactus Blossoms' song "Mississippi" was featured in episode 3 of "Twin Peaks: The Return," which aired on @Showtime on May 28, 2017.

Credits
Guests – Page Burkum and Jack Torrey of @TheCactusBlossoms
